<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Din" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Din,</orth> subst. loud noise: <cit><quote>beasts shall tremble at thy d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.371" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 371</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.314" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 314</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.1.178" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 1, 178</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.200" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 200</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.2.119" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 2, 119</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 3.3.20" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.4.111" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 4, 111</bibl>. Per. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.0." default="NO" valid="yes">III Prol. 2</bibl>. <cit><quote>trumpeters, with brazen d. blast you the city's ear,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 4.8.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 8, 36</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>minstrelsy and pretty d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 5.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. V, 2, 7</bibl></cit>.
